</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-30_ pf-text-1">Children with sickle cell are susceptible to complications such as pain crises, infections, and acute chest syndrome, which require immediate attention (CDC, 2022).
































